General.Name: Palram
General.Description: Palram Industries (1990) Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells thermoplastic sheets, and panel systems, and finished products in Israel and internationally. The company offers PVC, polycarbonate and acrylic sheets, and panel systems. Its products are used in DIY, construction, architectural project, advertising, agriculture, safety and security, and fabrication markets. The company was founded in 1963 and is based in Zevulun, Israel. Palram Industries (1990) Ltd is a subsidiary of Ramat Yohanan Industries & Agriculture Development-Agricultural Coperative Society.
